AGI - It is all to clarify the tragedy that was consumed last night, around 23.30, in a house of the hamlet of Campo a mare>&nbsp; in Teramano, where lives a family native to the countries of Eastern Europe. The agonizing body of a 16-year-old was found by the 12-year-old brother in the bedroom. When the rescuers of 118 arrived on the spot, unfortunately there was nothing left to do for the boy. It is enough to understand that the 16-year-old had removed his life by strangling > with a belt for clothes. But it is not clear whether it is a voluntary gesture or rather a tragic game.
&nbsp;
It is not in fact excluded that the 16-year-old may have participated in a 'challenge' in a videochat> or online games in which members would be induced to provoke injuries, up to extreme gestures. At the disposal of the judicial authority the carabinieri seized the personal computer and the cell phone of the boy, while the psalm was transferred to the morgue of the hospital of Teramo and made available to the pm for the autopsy. From a first on the corpse, the anatomicalologist did not detect bruises or traces of shells that could cause a violent death.
&nbsp;
Family members do not explain the reasons for the gesture: the 16-year-old, who has not written anything about his suicidal will, has been described by his teachers as a student with excellent school results and respectful and calm behaviors.> The investigations are entrusted to the carabinieri, the Prosecutor of Teramo has however opened a file against unknown to allow the carrying out of investigations to 360 degrees.

