To the Centre? In the morning stable time on all regions with alternating cloudyness to lightened, weak rains on Tuscany. In the afternoon still dry time with calm skies or little cloudy everywhere. In the evening and nighty cloudy rising with local rains on Tuscany, dry elsewhere. Minimum and maximum temperatures in a slight decrease. Winds weak or moderate by south-eastern quadrants. Husbands moved or very moved.
&nbsp;
To the South and the Islands:> In the morning dry time with serene or little cloudy skies on all sectors. In the afternoon stable time with skies mostly peaceful everywhere. In the evening and night we renew conditions of dry time with scattered clouds and wide clear, weak rains coming on Sardinia. Minimum and maximum temperatures in rise. Winds weak or moderate by southern quadrants. Very moved or agitated husbands.&nbsp;

